Alien::SFML version 0.01 SFML 2.0 RC
====================================

This module installs SFML 2.0 RC

INSTALLATION

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Perl

Alien::Base
Alien::CMake

If you are on linux, you will need (according to the SFML website) dev packages for:

    pthread
    opengl
    xlib
    xrandr
    freetype
    glew
    jpeg
    sndfile
    openal

